.claude

# TLS material: keys are gitignored but listed here as defense-in-depth so a
# working tree that happens to have a leftover PEM can't accidentally bake
# the key into a published image. ACME issuance (services/tlsAcme) writes
# certs into a bind-mounted volume at runtime.
infra/docker/tls
infra/docker/uploads
infra/docker/data
infra/docker/mail
# Frontend bundles are produced inside the nginx build stage now; never
# ship any prior local output.
infra/docker/static
